# 🌍 Language Translator – CodeAlpha AI Task

A professional desktop application that translates text between 15+ languages using Google Translate.  
Built with Python, Tkinter, and `deep-translator`.  
Developed as part of my **CodeAlpha Artificial Intelligence Internship**.

